The design proscess at the begining was a ragtag group throwing ideas at the wall to see what sticks
After such a lukewarm presentation created thanks to a pressure to show something, the focus was shifted to diablo as nearly the whole team working on starcraft went to help make Diablo, leaving only one of the origonal team on the project as they set out to overhaul the game. The engine was rebuilt from scratch to allow more options, and they had to work around thier technical limitations to build thier art